==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Godless
<hw>God"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having, or acknowledging, no God;
without reverence for God; impious; wicked.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>God"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>God"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Godlike</ent>⟦br⟧
